comment._content: First I must say what the San Diego Aero Space Museum is doing by sharing all these wonderful images is nothing short of fabulous and most generous! That said, I will venture to say that the man on the left is Al "Fronty" Nichols, (continuing left to right) Bon MacDougall, Al Johnson, and unknown. The last one I have never seen before, but surely someone else has.
